rComments: Shannon is really nice, but she talks very fast. You need to go to class, her slides have a fair amount of info but what she says in class is what matters the most. Theres surprise quizzes that drag your mark to the grave. Her midterm was extremely easy, but her exam was tough, and she doesn't post past exams. Be careful! You can get a 70+ easily.
teacherRatingTags: ['Beware of pop quizzes', 'Gives good feedback', "Skip class? You won't pass."]
